content.text:
Almost there! Two things:

### 1. Line 29 — still using user's title
You still have `${title}` on line 29. Change it to `${data.data.title}` — that's the whole point of this task, use Jikan's title instead of trusting the user.

### 2. Missing closing `}` for `addFavorite`
The function needs to be closed. After line 39 (the `)`), you need:
- A `.catch()` for the whole fetch chain (to handle network errors)
- Then a closing `}` for the `addFavorite` function

So after line 39 it should look like:

